<header class="page-header"><h1 class='page-title'>Careers</h1></header>	</header><!-- #masthead -->
	
		<section id="main" class="site-main clearfix">
		<div class="site-wrapper wrap">
		
	<div id="primary" class="content-area">
		<div id="content" class="site-content" role="main">
		
										
				<article id="post-4033" class="post-4033 page type-page status-publish hentry no-thumbnail">
	<header class="entry-header">
			</header>
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<div class="wpb_row vc_row-fluid">
	<div class="vc_span8 wpb_column column_container">
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			
	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<h1><strong>We&#8217;re Building the Future of Entertainment.</strong></h1>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We’ve created a frictionless platform for our users to design, script and publish their creations. We call it the Imagination Platform™. Here at ROBLOX, it’s our job to facilitate and support our users’ creativity, and that’s no easy task.</span></p>
<p><strong> Are you ready for a challenge? </strong></p>
<p><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9RiNEaGUHI0" width="853" height="480" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p>
<h2>ROBLOX is looking for brilliant people to join us in creating the ultimate Imagination Platform™.</h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Every day our employees are on a mission, pioneering a new industry, taking risks and working on a diverse number of complex problems not available at other tech companies.</span></p>
<p><strong>The Product:</strong></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The ROBLOX Imagination Platform™ is a vibrant ecosystem of creators, builders, game players, and adventurers imagining with their friends. Our ROBLOX Studio IDE allows powerful and intuitive creation, published with a single click to the cloud, and instantly playable with your friends across PC, Mac, iOS, Android, Xbox and Oculus Rift. Integrated matchmaking, persistence, and billing support provide developers rich functionality for building great games and experiences. The ROBLOX.com website ties this ecosystem together with search and discovery, social networking, and a massive catalog of user made content.</span></p>
<p><strong>The Technology:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><i><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">We are a cloud services provider for our developers, seamlessly scaling behind creations as they gain usage and popularity. </span></i></i></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">Our technology provides solutions across multiple verticals, social networking, search, ecommerce, analytics, data persistence, security, ad delivery and real-time bidding.</span></i></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">The game engine has a powerful and efficient C++ core, plugging into a cutting edge custom rendering engine, a replication framework, and a custom physics engine capable of simulating articulated bodies as well as collisions</span></i></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">Platform specific shells encapsulates the game engine on PC, Mac, iOS, Android, Amazon Devices, Xbox and Oculus Rift</span></i></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">On the platform layer, we handle 500,000 requests per second.</span></i></li>
</ul>
